POM FILE - Project Object Model; always be in the root of your project.
    1. Project Meta Data (project name, versions).
    2. Dependencies ( list of the projects we depend on).
    3. Plug-ins (JUnit testing reports etc).



PROJECT COORDINATES:
    1. This helps us identifying the project.
    2. Group ID - Name of company (reverse url).
    3. Artifact ID - name of the project.
    4. Version - Release version .


ADDING DEPENDENCIES:
    1. Once we have something to be added we will add a dependencies.
    2. dependency will be acting as a parent to groupID, artifactID, and version (optional).
    3. GAV - GroupID, ArtifactID, and Version.
    4. search.maven a best website to get the GAV.


